Thank you Manorama Online for having me join this esteemed panel alongside @sivan_santosh @supriyamenonprithviraj @shankarspage @sonylivindia ‘s @saugatam @ratheesh_balakrishnan_poduval to discuss the Blurring Lines of Regional Entertainment. 

This was the Fifth Edition of Kerala's marquee Digital Summit. 

#ManoramaOnline
#MO@25 
#JainOnline 
#techspectations @techspectations @manoramaonline #entertainment #film #breakingboundaries #entrepreneur

Namaskaaram 🕉️🙏🏻 

A long time wish (mom’s especially) comes true.. had an amazing experience at the much revered MahaShivratri celebrations at @isha.foundation .. but what made it most special was when @sadhguru remembered me from when we had met in Dubai last year for the #savesoil initiative for which he has traveled all over the world meeting world leaders to stress the importance of retaining what is left our top soil as it’s nearing depletion therefore deeming it unfit for the preservation of vital and natural resources and vegetation which is important to mankind and future generations. I would only be bewildered if His vibration doesn’t affect you. I love the spirit with which he does good work and imparts good messages and needless to say the music, dance, joy & positive vibe that he maintains at all times. 

This was also a rare opportunity to listen to the chief guest of the evening. President of India, Smt. Droupadi Murmur’s speech on her views on spirituality and the meaning behind the entity Lord Shiva, and her experiences with Sadhguru. 

From getting His blessings, holding his hands, his tap on my shoulder urging me, rather all us young folks to “TAKE THE GOOD WORD FORWARD AND MAKE IT HAPPEN”, chanting Lord shiv slokas, dancing with @sadhguru  in front of the mighty #adiyogi and perfectly sealing it with midnight #meditation with Sadhguru… It was so magical and an unforgettable night for me and my parents. 

I thank Isha foundation team for extending this invitation to us and a bigger thanks to all the volunteers who assisted us all night. (Archana/Lakshmi Akka and especially Anjali 💃🏻 - love you girl 😄🥰)
Thanks @nabel_marketer for coordinating it for us.

#isha #ishafoundation #adiyogi #sadhguru #mahashivratri #mahashivratri2023 #spirituality #droupadimurmu #presidentofindia #president #chanting #shivratri #lordshiva #celebration

Blissed out to a point of disaster?!

When Sheer negligence along with ignorance, and innocence combined with the an immense lack of knowledge about safety and guidelines & zero common sense about how to be responsible for both self and others come together.. we have a Thanoor boat incident. My heart goes out to the victims who lost their lives and warm condolences to the families. Also saddened to hear that this has taken together the lives of one entire family. 

We now have an absconding boat owner who had converted a fishing boat to a passenger tourist boat with absolutely no safety features on it, plus this one’s totally ridiculous .. the boat had NO LICENSE either to operate with passengers on board. 

Respect and more power to all those who have been working tirelessly since last night in rescue operations. 

Inspite of having several incidents like these in our country time n time again… we end up settling on this thought… 
പോയവർക്ക് പോയി. ഇനിയെങിലും മാറ്റവും റൂൾസും വരുമോ? 

#desperate #needforchange #godknows #accident #kerala #norules #norulesjustlips #alltalk #thisisbullshit #ignorance #malabar #kerala

Are the Innocent becoming victims of OD-d unpredictable minds? Seems unsafe to have such loose & volatile people around us. This cannot be ignored anymore. This is Another example of lack of safety measures & commonsense from higher authorities. Ridiculous. That too Within the same week!!!

RIP Dr. Vandana Das. Deepest condolences to her parents. Can’t imagine what they are going through. The only child they had. 

Like I said in a post earlier this week.. പോയവർക്ക് പോയി. 😞 

Repeated incidents.. nothing ever changes. Everything just gets forgotten.. where is our system or those who lay them out, in all this? 
Huge reformations needed.. but when.. by who.. one can only live in hope in this country or die trying. 

Another thing that has always haunted me is .. why isn’t a very BIG FAT OBVIOUS murder with so many eye witnesses dealt with an immediate punishment / consequence? Just KILL THE MORON! I don’t get it. 🤷🏻‍♀️

‘Mine against me’ leads to Lupus and(or) other autoimmune disorders. 
With real heroes of @lupustrustindia who need to strive really hard to make each waking day feel normal… turn the certain unpredictability of each day into a lesser burden.. who need to accept gracefully and remind themselves to slow down because they are aware that they can’t keep up with the rest of the world…  Here’s more power to those who live in this uncertainty… to those conquering Lupus… creating awareness of this lesser known condition. 
Thank you for making me feel ‘belonged’ as part of your family & especially to Dr. Shenoy and Vachas🦋 for being such a support to me as well. 

#lupus #autoimmune #disorder #bodyfightsitself #createawareness

Thank you Dr. Kaveri for talking from your personal experience…  stories like yours and others like you about how you use social media as a useful tool to help others, while ignoring haters and nasty, disrespectful comments is very vital. Im so happy that you are able to see what we were trying to convey by making this film. This is your film ladies.. your story. Write your own! 

Every woman is a hero… As Dr. Amala Sreeram calls it HEROINISM. 

Sadly there is no such word in the dictionary… but why can’t we make it when others gladly fake it. 
There’s a saying ‘fake it till you make it’ … but let that not be at the expense of someone else’s peace or happiness.
